article_title: Hagedorn endorsed for second run against Walz
article_text:
Owatonna, MN (55060)

Today

Rain this morning with thunderstorms by evening. High 76F. Winds SE at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 100%..

Tonight

Cloudy skies this evening followed by thunderstorms late. A few storms may be severe. Low near 60F. Winds E at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 90%.

WILLIAM MORRIS
wmorris@owatonna.com

og.description: OWATONNA — Southern Minnesota voters will see some familiar faces this year vying for the seat of Minnesota’s First Congressional District.
